Class GetterSetterExtension

java.lang.Object
bluej.extensions2.Extension
GetterSetterExtension
public class GetterSetterExtension
extends bluej.extensions2.Extension
This extension help to: 1) Generate source code of GET/SET methods of all class's properties 2) Generate source code of GET method of one propertie 3) Generate source code of SET method of one propertie 4) Generate GUI JavaFX to view/edit object's properties with GET/SET methods
Version:
0.0000000000000001 --> Math.sin(Math.PI-Double.MIN_VALUE) --> :)
Author:
(Milton Jesús Vera Contreras - miltonjesusvc@ufps.edu.co)
